Scenario: As a movie collector I must be able to interact with an empty collection so I can start up a new collection.

Given the collection is empty
When I list the movies
Then the list of movies should look like
Your collection is empty.

Given the collection is empty
When I add movies Jaws, Star Wars and Alien
When I list the movies
Then the list of movies should look like
Jaws
Star Wars
Alien
Number of movies in the collection 3.
